    General Stores in Kandivali East, Mumbai

    (1091 Ratings & Reviews) 4.0 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Kandivali East, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These retail stores are a part of the sales network of most FMCG brands and leading manufacturing companies. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Kandivali East, Mumbai from the list given above.
